B.a0g=new A.dz("Poshtiban Yar","poshtiban_yar","Poshtiban Yar is an Android application designed to support POS-device management. It allows users to submit the status of POS devices and locate assigned devices on a map. The app utilizes the camera to capture pictures of devices and provides a map interface to show device locations. Additionally, Poshtiban Yar includes features for marketing and finding new customers, enabling users to expand their client base efficiently.\n            ",B.Vq,"Farazpardazan","farazpardazan","poshtiban_yar")
